Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Pangasinan College of Fisheries in the Municipality of Binmaley, Province of Pangasinan, to Binmaley School of Fisheries
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 328
An Act Changing the Name of the Pangasinan College of Fisheries in the Municipality of Binmaley, Province of Pangasinan, to Binmaley School of Fisheries
Section 1. The name of the Pangasinan College of Fisheries, located in the Municipality of Binmaley, Province of Pangasinan, is changed to Binmaley School of Fisheries.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
